data.description: This home has just been reduced almost $35,000!  Waiting for you! This elegant spacious 2 story home offers 4 BRS 2 .5 baths 3 car garage.  Location! Location! The fully fenced backyard backs up to an easement and then to the Plank Walking Trail! Two story chandeliered foyer is bordered by arched entryways to oversized Living Rm & Dining Rm--- with views of Fam Rm Keystone-trim gas fireplace. The entertainment/relaxing factor continues to the Breakfast Area and then to expansive kitchen area with granite counters, breakfast bar, and double oven.  Newer stainless appliances include: 2 yr Thermador refrig, MWO, & 36" Thermador 5 burner cooktop. (New Kohler kitchen faucet)! The pantry and Service closet are next to the convenient laundry room where you will find newer front load LG W&D, cabinet enclosed laundry tub, and exit door to 3 car garage.   Hardwood stairs lead to 4 spacious upper level bedrooms, (with multiple walk in closets). MBR includes: 17x13 W/I closet and 13x10 ensuite sitting area nestled by turret styled windows; UL oversized baths with Corian-type vanities; Skylit Master bath with whirlpool tub and private commode. Lest we forget the finished basement: Separate rec room and additional rooms offer lots of options!  Additional high-end features include: Custom ceilings; 4" millwork and 6 panel doors; rounded wall corners, hardwood floors with contrasting wood inlays, 9 ft ceilings on Main Level with strategically placed recessed lighting offering a clean and unobtrusive look!   Nutone Intercom throughout home (and it works);  Maintenance free backyard fence;  Garage sensor lighting and Newer Liftmaster door openers with smart cameras.......     Discover the perfect blend of comfort, style, and functionality - this home awaits.........YOU!
